span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>οὐ γάρ μοι σθεναρὴν χεῖρ’ ἐπέ [θηκε μάτην] \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>αλλ’ ἐν ἐμοὶ καμάτων εὗρεν τέλ [ος ἔσχε τ’ἄγαλμα] \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ἀγχόθι λαϊνέης αὔλακος ὑδρο [φόρου] \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>τὴν αὐτὸς ποίησεν, ἐς ἠέρα πολλ [ὸν ἀείρας] \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>νᾶμα φέρειν καθαρὸν ἐνναέται [ς Κατὰνης] \u003Cbr id=\"al7-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.8)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"\n                        Ἐννοΐου\n                    \">  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἐννοΐου\">Ἐννοΐου\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.7)\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"file":365,"uri":365,"title":366,"status":367,"editionAuthor":11,"type":368,"objectType":369,"material":370,"condition":24,"layoutDesc":371,"handNote":375,"date":384,"places":388,"geo":391,"country":162,"region":163,"settlement":57,"repository":393,"idno":394,"textLang":396,"facsimile":398,"provenance":53,"letterHeights":400,"publications":401,"zotero":402,"keywords":403,"html":407},"ISic001279","Edict of Flavius Felix Eumathus regarding the Thermae Achillianae",{"_":10},{"_":198,"ana":199,"ref":200},{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},{"layout":372},{"p":373,"rs":374,"damage":24},"Greek text over four lines. The fourth line is shorter than the\n                                        other three and ends with a vacat. The letters are broadly regular and neatly\n                                        cut, but the sizing and spacing varies considerably across the four lines.",{"_":29,"ana":30,"ref":31},{"lettering":376,"dimensions":377},"Letters are wide and omicron, phi, sigma, epsilon and theta are, on\n                                    occasion formed by overlarge circles. Epsilon, sigma and omega are lunate. Xsi is\n                                    formed in a distinctive, ornate fashion. Interpuncts are used occasionally, and\n                                    formed of an 's' shape, sometimes forward, sometimes backward facing. Numerals are\n                                    marked with a supraline.",[378,381],{"type":36,"l":379,"from":38,"to":144,"h":380,"unit":41},"Line 1-4","44-62",{"type":43,"l":382,"from":38,"to":144,"h":383,"unit":41},"Lines 1-4","9-27",{"_":385,"notBefore":386,"notAfter":386,"evidence":387},"434 CE (reporting an edict from the consuls of 433)",434,"internal-date",[389,390],{"_":53,"type":54,"ref":55},{"_":57,"type":58,"ref":59},[392],[62,63],{"_":165,"role":68,"ref":166},{"_":395,"type":72},"265",{"_":288,"mainLang":285,"languages":397},[288],{"n":78,"url":399,"height":174,"width":231,"desc":232,"surfaceType":83},"ISic001279_tiled.tif",[],[296,87,87,297,297,297,298,298,178,299,89,94,237],[303,99,99,304,304,304,305,305,182,306,101,106,240],[404,405,406,198,17,21,113,114,189,190,114,191,362,285],"isic001279","edict of flavius felix eumathus regarding the thermae achillianae",{"_":10},"\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span> Φλάβιος Φῆλιξ Εὐμάθιος ὁ λαμπρ[ότατος ὑπατικὸς τῆς Σικελῶν ἐπα]ρχίας εἶπεν · αἱ θερμαὶ αἱ Ἀχιλλιαναὶ ἐξ ἀρ[χ]αίας διατυπώσεως ἀνήλ \u003Cspan class=\"underline\">ω\u003C/span> [σαν πήσας \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span> καθ’? ἑκάστην? ἡμέραν? \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>ιούσης τῆς ἐπισκευῆς ἐ [πιμελείᾳ? Φλαβίου?] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan clas